{"commentv2": 1, "number": 0, "id": 3229377, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "varenne", "body": "Related to the Star Lake Amphitheater event in Ardenweald \n\n\n[achievement=14353] minigude: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sQonxU4IzRM\nHow the whole process looks in 1 day (repeat 7 times): https://youtu.be/IiAxdA8q44Y\n\n[ul]\n[li][b]Players with Night Fae covenant can speak with [npc=171743]  and activate the fight. [/b]\nYou need to [b]activate Anima Conductor link[/b] of the day to the Star Lake Amphitheater area.\nAnima Conductor is located in the Hear of the Forest main Night Fae covenant base. [b]MORE INFO [url=https://www.wowhead.com/guides/anima-conductor-covenant-sanctum-improvements-shadowlands]HERE[/url][/b][/li]\n[li]After you speak with the [npc=171743]  he summons one out of 7 rares\n[quote]/way 41.46, 44.83 Speak with Dapperdew (Star Lake Amphitheater)[/quote]\n\n[ul]\n[li][npc=166135][/li]\n[li][npc=166145][/li]\n[li][npc=166142][/li]\n[li][npc=166139][/li]\n[li][npc=166138][/li]\n[li][npc=166146][/li]\n[li][npc=166140][/li]\n[/ul]\nEach rare is available whole day and you can re summon it.\n[/li]\n[li]Right now the [b]reward[/b] is [achievement=14353] and [achievement=14309] score\nAnd there is also a vendor that unlocks items after each kill:  [npc=163714] \n[b]/way 42.75 46.03 Master Clerk Salorn (Reward vendor)[/b]\nMaster Clerk Salorn location: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q3Ek4oH3z8A\nThe final reward, after you kill all 7 rares is [item=180748]\nOther loot:\n[item=181304]\n[item=180416]\n[item=180417]\n[item=180418]\n[item=180419]\n[item=175069]\n[item=175095]\n[item=182175]\n[/li]\n\n[/ul]", "date": "2020-09-11T22:53:08-05:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2020-10-12T08:19:04-05:00", 1, "varenne"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 1, "id": 3232754, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Boxofbeer", "body": "[b][npc=166146][/b] rare mob can be found in [b][zone=11510][/b].\n[ul]\n[li][b]Location[/b]: 41.51 44.82[/li]\n[li][b]Required for[/b]: [achievement=14353] [/li]\n[li][b]Rare drop: [/b][b][item=180748][/b] (unlocks after defeating all 7 encounters) [/li]\n[/ul]\nTo trigger [b][npc=166146][/b] event you have to be in the Night Fae covenant.\nIn Heart of the Forest use [b]Anima Conductor[/b] and channel anima to [b]Dreamsong Fenn[/b]. There's a rare mark should appear on the map.\nMake you way there. To summon [b][npc=166146][/b] you need to speak to [b][npc=171743][/b] on the stage. But there's a problem.\nOther mob may be summoned instead - one of the [b][achievement=14353][/b] mobs. They rotate every day, so you need to visit npc until you get [b][npc=166146][/b].\n[quote]This is \"personal\" rare mob, only you can summon it after linking Dreamsong Fenn and Anima Conductor. Other players cant even talk to [b][npc=171743][/b] / summon rares. At least on beta.[/quote]\n\n[quote][u][b]TomTom coordinates:[/b][/u]\n\n/way 41.51 44.82 Niya As Xavius Location (Random)\n[/quote]\n\n[npc=166146] rare mob location - https://youtu.be/AhmcBbBxAqE", "date": "2020-09-24T20:48:14-05:00", "rating": -2, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2020-10-01T13:09:31-05:00", 4, "Boxofbeer"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 2, "id": 3232837, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Sipder2", "body": "[npc=166146] is 1 of 7 random rares in the Star Lake Amphitheater.\n\n[npc=166135].\n[npc=166138].\n[npc=166139].\n[npc=166142].\n[npc=166140].\n[npc=166145].\n[npc=166146].\n\n[b]How to summon [npc=166146][/b]:\n\n[ol]\n[li]be a member of the Night Fae Covenant[/li]\n[li]complete the First Chapter in the Night Fae Campaign (For Queen and Grove!) until unlock the Sanctum Reservoir[/li]\n[li]speak with [npc=167289] in Heart of the Forest to unlock the Anima Conductor rank 1[/li]\n[li]speak with [npc=167196] to grab the quest [quest=60723][/li]\n[li]use Anima Conductor and channel anima to Dreamsong Fenn[/li]\n[li]go to Star Lake Amphitheater and speak with [npc=171743] to start the event and summon a random rare[/li]\n[/ol]\n\n/way 38.6, 55.3 Zayhad (lower level)\n/way 50,4, 63,8 Sesselie (lower level)\n\n/way 41,5, 44,8 Star Lake Amphitheater\n\nNotes:\nIf [npc=171743] don't call [npc=166146], wait the daily reset and try again until she calls [npc=166146].\nTo unlock the Anima Conductor you need 1k [currency=1813] and 1x [currency=1810].\n\n[b]Video guide[/b]: https://youtu.be/CRDdQ8vMVGI", "date": "2020-09-25T08:06:05-05:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2020-10-07T12:13:21-05:00", 7, "Sipder2"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 3, "id": 3259310, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Calesta", "body": "[url=https://shadowlands.wowhead.com/npc=166146/niya-as-xavius]Niya, As Xavius[/url] is a silver dragon elite sometimes starring in the Star Lake Amphitheater of Ardenweald and is the target for one of the special encounters needed to complete the [url=https://shadowlands.wowhead.com/achievement=14309/adventurer-of-ardenweald]Adventurer of Ardenweald[/url], [url=https://shadowlands.wowhead.com/achievement=14353/ardenwealds-a-stage]Ardenweald's a Stage[/url], and [url=https://shadowlands.wowhead.com/achievement=14504/niya-as-xavius]Niya, As Xavius[/url] achievements.\r\n\r\nIf you are a member of the Night Fae covenant and have unlocked the first tier of the Anima Conductor within the Sanctum, then activate the stream to the Dreamsong Fenn and talk to [url=https://shadowlands.wowhead.com/npc=171743/dapperdew]Dapperdew[/url] to start one of the following special encounters.\r\n\r\n[quote]/way 41.50, 44.82 Dapperdew[/quote]\r\n\r\n[ul]\r\n[li][url=https://shadowlands.wowhead.com/npc=166135/astra-as-azshara]Astra, As Azshara[/url][/li]\r\n[li][url=https://shadowlands.wowhead.com/npc=166145/dreamweaver-as-nzoth]Dreamweaver, As N'Zoth[/url][/li]\r\n[li][url=https://shadowlands.wowhead.com/npc=166142/glimmerdust-as-jaina]Glimmerdust, As Jaina[/url][/li]\r\n[li][url=https://shadowlands.wowhead.com/npc=166139/glimmerdust-as-kiljaeden]Glimmerdust, As Kil'jaeden[/url][/li]\r\n[li][url=https://shadowlands.wowhead.com/npc=166138/mikai-as-argus-the-unmaker]Mi'kai, As Argus[/url][/li]\r\n[li][url=https://shadowlands.wowhead.com/npc=166146/niya-as-xavius]Niya, As Xavius[/url][/li]\r\n[li][url=https://shadowlands.wowhead.com/npc=166140/senthii-as-guldan]Senthii, As Gul'dan[/url][/li]\r\n[/ul]\r\n\r\nShe starts with a funny introduction that's yelled to all of the theatergoers.  \r\n\r\n[quote]Attention fellow lovers of the arts! Through the generous patronage of Calesta, I am pleased to announce a new performance shall begin shortly in Star Lake Amphitheater!\r\n\r\nIn this brilliant display of theatre, one of our own players will transform before your very eyes into a mighty foe from another realm, ready to do battle with any brave enough to challenge them!\r\n\r\nRemember, it is through the support of our patrons and viewers like you that we have anima enough to pursue the creative arts! And now, without further ado...[/quote]\r\n\r\nThe adversary is then revealed and appears on stage.", "date": "2020-11-28T13:13:50-06:00", "rating": 6, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
