{"commentv2": 1, "number": 1, "id": 2494843, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Anatta", "body": "When engaged solo, Shade of Xavius will not use his [url=http://www.wowhead.com/spell=212834/nightmare-bolt]Nightmare Bolt[/url] ability. This means that he can be killed by a single player, provided they can keep themselves alive through his other attacks.\r\n\r\nFor what it's worth, an 890 equipped bear druid with 17% leech from gear can do it on Mythic difficulty.", "date": "2017-05-16T21:02:44-05:00", "rating": 4, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
